      "description": "Hey there! I'm super excited to help this awesome car find its next adventure! It\u2019s been a fantastic, reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. It drives like a dream and has been well-cared for. I\u2019m looking for a quick sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to chat!",
