    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The suspension geometry remains true, featuring upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein monotube dampers. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all six cylinders remain within factory tolerances. A mechanically sound specimen for the enthusiast who prioritizes turn-in response and powertrain linearity.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Reliable daily driver. Title in hand.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
