    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish and has been regularly waxed, though a few minor stone chips are visible on the front bumper and hood from standard highway use. The body is straight with no major dings or scratches. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean; the leather upholstery is free of tears, showing only light softening and minor creasing on the driver's side bolster. All cabin technology, including the infotainment screen, backup camera, and heated seats, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It has a documented service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. Recently, the brake pads were replaced and the tires were rotated, showing approximately 70% tread life remaining. This car has been a reliable companion and is ready for its next owner without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
